  • Health Impact: Average of 0.1 estimated respiratory cases per day

Key Characteristics

  • Small but growing healthcare (new medical college investment)
  • Mountain capital advantages (cleaner air than valleys)
  • Kohima will show how climate change affects respiratory health even in smaller mountain capitals
